item.dc:creator: @Fireskrit Fireskrit
item.description:
@Fireskrit wrote:

Is this the online client or a downloaded one?

If it is downloaded try using the online one because it seems as though the downloadable ones dont have every silab item to begin with.

Just go to: http://client.silabsoft.org/ and it will work everytime. ;D

Other than that… I have no expertise with homemade clients. Seems as though most ppl who code them don’t do it properly.
